<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abraham's Blog</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/</link><description/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.inshomepgup.com/categories/vue/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Vue3 特性学习</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3-%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3-%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</guid><description>&lt;p>从Vue2 过渡到Vue3，有挺多方面还是不一样的，大部分还是提升了效率，可以更专注于业务的开发。&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category><category>Vue3</category></item><item><title>Vue3插槽的使用</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3%E6%8F%92%E6%A7%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3%E6%8F%92%E6%A7%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="插槽">插槽
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>组件的灵活性很大一部分都来源于插槽（Slot），这大大提升了组件的可复用性和扩展性。它允许父组件在子组件的预留位置中插入任意内容。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在React里，类似的功能是通过 &lt;code>props.children&lt;/code> 实现的，可以直接将JSX片段作为属性传递。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="默认插槽">默认插槽
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>当子组件只定义一个匿名插槽时，父组件传递的所有内容都会被放置在这个插槽中。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>子组件 (&lt;code>ChildComponent.vue&lt;/code>)&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">class&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;default-slot&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">h3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>子组件标题&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">h3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>如果父组件没有提供内容，我将作为后备内容显示。&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>父组件使用&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ChildComponent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>这是从父组件传递过来的内容，它将替换掉子组件的后备内容。&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ChildComponent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="具名插槽">具名插槽
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>当我们需要在子组件的不同位置插入不同内容时，就需要使用具名插槽。通过为 &lt;code>slot&lt;/code> 元素添加 &lt;code>name&lt;/code> 属性，我们可以定义多个插槽。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>子组件 (&lt;code>LayoutComponent.vue&lt;/code>)&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">class&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;container&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">header&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;header&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">header&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">main&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c">&amp;lt;!-- 这是一个默认插槽 --&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">main&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">footer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;footer&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">footer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>父组件使用&lt;/strong>
在父组件中，我们使用 &lt;code>v-slot&lt;/code> 指令并带上插槽的名字来指定内容的目标插槽。&lt;code>v-slot&lt;/code> 有一个简写形式 &lt;code>#&lt;/code>。&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category><category>Vue3</category><category>Slot</category></item><item><title>pinia 插件 pinia-plugin-persistedstate-2的使用</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/pinia/pinia-plugin-persistedstate-2/pinia-plugin-persistedstate-2%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Sat, 08 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/pinia/pinia-plugin-persistedstate-2/pinia-plugin-persistedstate-2%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p>pinia-plugin-persistedstate 和 pinia-plugin-persistedstate-2 都是持久化插件。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这里选用 -2的这个包，是因为可以自定义持久化使用的set和get方法。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/InsHomePgup/pic_go_img/main/blog/20250208153253271.png"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这里的默认get set还是使用的 json 的序列化
如果能自定义序列化函数，那么可以使用另外一个缓存工具&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/localforage" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>localforage&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这个缓存的特点是支持promise的异步调用。还有降级使用，优先使用更领先的存储方案，indexedDB。如果当前的浏览器不支持的话，再降级使用localStorage&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>indexedDB&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-ts" data-lang="ts">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">pinia&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">createPinia&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">pinia&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">use&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">createPersistedStatePlugin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">({&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">storage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">getItem&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">async&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">localforage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">getItem&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">setItem&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">async&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">value&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">localforage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">setItem&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">value&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">removeItem&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">async&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">localforage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">removeItem&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}))&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description><category>Vue</category><category>Pinia</category><category>Cache</category></item><item><title>Vue渲染机制</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/render/vue%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/render/vue%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://cn.vuejs.org/guide/extras/rendering-mechanism" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>渲染机制&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>虚拟DOM，Virtual DOM&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category></item><item><title>Hash路由和History路由</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/hash%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%92%8Chistory%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/hash%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%92%8Chistory%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</guid><description>&lt;p>监听hash改变的函数
&lt;a class="link" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/hashchange_event" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>onHashChange&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>hash路由：
监听hash url 的变化，来渲染内容。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>history路由：
使用 History API 控制路由&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category><category>Vue-Router</category></item></channel></rss>